::Hot Rod/Prowl::

Prowl and Hot Rod listened to their story, as the Autobots arrived.
Prowl rehashed, "So you got into some trouble at the academy, and were
shipped out. After that what exactly lead you here?"
Hot Rod was quiet, he had gotton in trouble so many times like that when
he was younger. Ultra Magnus, Springer, Kup, and even Optimus Prime
himself were always after him, he remembered.

::Epyon/Skyburst::

Unsure of what to do they stand back, waiting to see if its a trick.
They let Alpha take care of Nightstrike.

OOC: We are standing outside a little room that is the cell that comes
off from the hall. They is just a break in the wall, that is where the
force field would be.
